  description: Azure unsheathes his sacred blade and activates the Sword Seal, increasing
    his Critical Rate by 70% for 1 turn before unleashing thousands of phantom strikes
    upon the enemy, dealing massive damage. If there is an enemy below 25% HP during
    battle, Azure unleashes the legendary Divine Assassination technique, increasing
    his Critical Rate by 75% for 2 turns before dealing massive damage.
